And you call yourself a Super Saiyan?

18
00:03:06,040 --> 00:03:08,740
<i>Freeza conceals bottomless power.</i>

19
00:03:08,780 --> 00:03:13,550
<i>Can it be that even with Vegeta's</i>
<i>explosive power-up, he is no match for Freeza?</i>

20
00:03:14,720 --> 00:03:20,880
<i>"How I've Waited for this Moment!!!</i>
<i>Son Goku Revived."</i>

21
