Running away?

22
00:04:19,410 --> 00:04:20,580
What?!

23
00:04:24,750 --> 00:04:27,350
No way!

24
00:04:34,030 --> 00:04:36,430
<i>His speed is...</i>

25
00:04:41,640 --> 00:04:45,770
Damn! To think that Freeza
still hasn't gone all-out yet...

26
00:04:45,810 --> 00:04:48,400
What a monster!

27
00:04:51,950 --> 00:04:56,880
Vegeta, quite frankly, using
the attacks and speed you just did,

28
00:04:56,920 --> 00:04:59,580
there's no way you can win against me.

29
00:05:03,630 --> 00:05:08,390
As I recall, you said something
about being a Super Saiyan.

30
00:05:08,430 --> 00:05:11,390
If you are as you say,

31
00:05:11,430 --> 00:05:15,770
does that mean that's the best
the "strongest in history" can do?

32
00:05:39,090 --> 00:05:42,290
<i>Up until this point, I could see him...</i>

33
00:05:50,670 --> 00:05:52,730
Don't make me laugh.

34
00:05:52,770 --> 00:05:59,680
The Super Saiyan is then no
more than a trivial legend after all.

35
00:05:59,720 --> 00:06:03,010
<i>Does this mean I've reached my limit?</i>

36
00:06:03,050 --> 00:06:07,050
<i>Have I not yet become a Super Saiyan?</i>

37
00:06:08,960 --> 00:06:14,620
<i>Or for that matter, is Freeza an</i>
<i>opponent not even a Super Saiyan can beat?</i>

38
00:06:17,730 --> 00:06:20,400
Nonsense! There's no
reason that should be so!

39
00:06:21,400 --> 00:06:23,070
Vegeta...

40
00:06:25,340 --> 00:06:28,070
How can such a thing be?!

41
00:06:29,680 --> 00:06:35,410
Such a thing... could never be!!

42
00:06:53,670 --> 00:06:55,400
<i>You fool.</i>

43
00:07:13,420 --> 00:07:14,410
I see you!

44
00:07:21,430 --> 00:07:23,420
I see you, Freeza!

45
00:07:47,660 --> 00:07:50,250
Vegeta, you...

46
00:08:28,660 --> 00:08:34,430
<i>Vegeta isn't blasting away blindly,</i>
<i>he's carefully aiming every shot!</i>

47
00:08:39,170 --> 00:08:43,240
<i>And yet Freeza is decidedly</i>
<i>keeping clear of them.</i>

48
00:08:43,280 --> 00:08:45,610
<i>They're both unbelievable!</i>

49
00:08:47,680 --> 00:08:48,940
Piccolo...

50
00:08:48,980 --> 00:08:51,220
Piccolo<i>-san...</i>

51
00:09:04,070 --> 00:09:05,400
What?!

52
00:09:35,030 --> 00:09:37,160
I-I am...

53
00:09:43,410 --> 00:09:48,740
I <i>am</i> a Super Saiyan!

54
00:09:49,740 --> 00:09:52,870
Burn in Hell, Freeza!

55
00:10:16,540 --> 00:10:20,530
Are you trying to destroy
the whole planet, Vegeta?!

56
00:10:36,320 --> 00:10:37,720
What?!

57
00:11:54,670 --> 00:11:56,500
It's just about time, I suppose.

58
00:11:56,540 --> 00:12:00,200
I can't have him getting too carried away.

59
00:12:03,140 --> 00:12:05,540
H-How could he...?

60
00:12:05,580 --> 00:12:11,710
He bounced all that
back with just a simple kick?!

61
00:12:11,750 --> 00:12:17,050
Vegeta had to have launched
that attack at his full power!

62
00:12:17,090 --> 00:12:20,690
He's incredible! He's more than incredible!

63
00:12:20,730 --> 00:12:26,070
And now, you will experience
a pain even greater than hell.

64
00:12:56,030 --> 00:13:00,300
This time, you'll let me lead off.

65
00:13:03,440 --> 00:13:05,240
Mildly.

66
00:13:13,780 --> 00:13:16,080
<i>Vegeta...</i>

67
00:13:16,120 --> 00:13:22,080
<i>For the first time in his life, Vegeta is</i>
<i>trembling, from the bottom of his heart.</i>

68
00:13:26,800 --> 00:13:31,760
<i>Both from genuine terror, and</i>
<i>from his conclusive frustration.</i>

69
00:13:35,640 --> 00:13:40,740
<i>He's even shedding tears</i>
<i>over his fright and hopelessness.</i>

70
00:13:40,780 --> 00:13:43,770
<i>This is another first.</i>

71
00:13:51,420 --> 00:13:54,080
Here goes. Are you ready?

72
00:14:24,290 --> 00:14:29,880
<i>Vegeta–Vegeta has</i>
<i>already lost the will to fight.</i>

73
00:14:51,750 --> 00:14:53,240
Vegeta!

74
00:15:01,490 --> 00:15:03,450
Don't!

75
00:15:03,490 --> 00:15:06,090
He's had it.

76
00:16:27,280 --> 00:16:31,740
Vegeta, I can't have
you giving up after so little.

77
00:16:31,780 --> 00:16:35,110
You'll have to go through more than this...

78
00:16:43,090 --> 00:16:46,080
...for a terror greater than hell's.

79
00:16:50,630 --> 00:16:56,060
Well? Have you started to
regret how foolish you've been?

80
00:16:56,100 --> 00:17:01,440
You lower-life-form, nothing-in-
your-mind-but-fighting Saiyan<i>-san</i>?

81
00:17:09,820 --> 00:17:13,650
I thought you at least were
different, and I pampered you,

82
00:17:13,690 --> 00:17:17,850
but you're just like the others who
performed their foolishness, aren't you?

83
00:17:23,030 --> 00:17:24,760
