84
00:17:24,800 --> 00:17:27,740
we would have gotten by
without having to go through this.

85
00:18:18,790 --> 00:18:21,760
V-Vegeta!

86
00:19:26,450 --> 00:19:29,690
If you want to save him, feel free at any time.

87
00:19:41,300 --> 00:19:42,800
<i>Piccolo and the others,</i>

88
00:19:42,840 --> 00:19:48,170
<i>faced with the terror of Freeza, whose</i>
<i>battle power is of a different dimension,</i>

89
00:19:48,210 --> 00:19:54,010
