<i>all three of them unable to move.</i>

90
00:20:04,630 --> 00:20:09,120
<i>Vegeta's ki is rapidly shrinking...</i>

91
00:20:09,160 --> 00:20:14,260
<i>and he was supposed to</i>
<i>have gotten incredibly stronger.</i>

92
00:20:14,300 --> 00:20:17,740
<i>Is this Freeza that strong?!</i>

93
00:20:23,740 --> 00:20:25,740
<i>I'm healed!</i>

94
00:21:17,470 --> 00:21:19,060
<i>I've gotten stronger!</i>

95
00:21:19,100 --> 00:21:22,430
<i>It's like the power is welling up inside!</i>

96
00:21:26,810 --> 00:21:31,540
<i>Unbelievable! And here</i>
<i>I thought I'd reached my limit.</i>

97
00:21:31,580 --> 00:21:34,070
<i>It's enough to scare me!</i>

98
00:21:35,080 --> 00:21:38,210
<i>But you know, it feels good!</i>

99
00:21:38,250 --> 00:21:41,380
<i>Even at a terrible time like this.</i>

100
00:21:41,420 --> 00:21:45,720
<i>My apologies, Gohan, Kuririn, and Piccolo!</i>

101
00:21:45,760 --> 00:21:49,420
<i>I'm coming now! Something</i>
<i>might just become of this!</i>

102
00:21:50,430 --> 00:21:52,930
<i>Goku at last recovers.</i>

103
00:21:52,970 --> 00:21:57,230
<i>How eagerly has this</i>
<i>moment been anticipated?</i>

104
00:22:02,040 --> 00:22:03,070
<i>You're the only one left</i>

105
00:22:03,110 --> 00:22:08,480
